<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The @@@D2Whirlwind@@@ Barbarian is a gear dependent character that is often used in PvP but can still have decent use in PvE. It is one of the most iconic builds in Diablo 2 and while it used to be one of the strongest builds in the game in earlier patches, it has been nerfed some but still has viability.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the @@@D2Whirlwind@@@ Barbarian. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Whirlwind@@@ - Main Damage dealer, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2LeapAttack@@@ - Useful for movement, required</li>
<li>20 points to Weapon Mastery of Choice - Adds Damage, Attack Rating, and Critical Strengthike</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2IncreasedSpeed@@@ - Helps you move faster, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2NaturalResistance@@@ - Massive boost to Resistances, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2BattleCommand@@@ - Increases Skills , required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2BattleOrders@@@ - Massive Life and Mana boosts, required</li>
<li>1+ points to @@@D2Shout@@@ - Increases Defenses, required</li>
</ol>

